OL,3,CGovernment's plans to shake up armed
OL,4,Cforces 'to be published in June'
OL,6,FThe long-awaited Strategic Defence
OL,7,FReview is expected to be published on
OL,8,For soon after Parliament returns from
OL,9,Frecess on Monday June 2, sources have
OL,10,Ftold ITV News.
OL,12,FThat is when military personnel and
OL,13,Fthe defence industry should learn just
OL,14,Fhow much of a shake-up of the armed
OL,15,Fforces the government has in mind.
OL,17,FThe review has gone through a number
OL,18,Fof iterations but is now believed to
OL,19,Fbe finished.
