OL,3,CGovernment's plans to shake up armed
OL,4,Cforces 'to be published in June'
OL,6,FIt is widely expected that the review
OL,7,Fwill call for much greater investment
OL,8,Fin hi-tech weaponry, particularly
OL,9,Fdrone and anti-drone systems, a shift
OL,10,Fthat is already underway as a result
OL,11,Fof the war in Ukraine.
OL,13,FSome commitments - such as the nuclear
OL,14,Fdeterrent, NATO membership and support
OL,15,Ffor Ukraine - are baked into the
OL,16,Freview's parameters.
