OL,6,FThe reviewers have also been asked to
OL,7,Flook at how to reinforce UK homeland
OL,8,Fsecurity with reports that a civilian
OL,9,F'Home Guard', separate from the
OL,10,FReserves, will be among the
OL,11,Frecommendations.
